o\": 5474}, {\"ngram\": \"wastewater\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5496}, {\"ngram\": \"manholes\", \"from\": 5509, \"to\": 5517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those blowbacks could become more severe and frequent as climate change powers stronger tropical storms and more flooding.\", \"from\": 5519, \"to\": 5641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those blowbacks\", \"from\": 5519, \"to\": 5534}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change powers\", \"from\": 5576, \"to\": 5597}, {\"ngram\": \"more flooding\", \"from\": 5627, \"to\": 5640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are getting squeezed here in Charleston between rapid and aggressive growth, a changing climate and rising sea levels,\\\" Wunderley said.\", \"from\": 5643, \"to\": 5782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5676, \"end\": 5686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\", \"score\": 0.999998469000992, \"rank\": 1.5310015348245155e-06, \"text\": \"Charleston\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rapid and aggressive growth\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5722}, {\"ngram\": \"Wunderley\", \"from\": 5767, \"to\": 5776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our infrastructure is also getting squeezed between those things.\", \"from\": 5783, \"to\": 5850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our infrastructure\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5802}, {\"ngram\": \"those things\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 5848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We really need as a community to invest in water and sewer upgrades.\\\"\", \"from\": 5851, \"to\": 5920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a community\", \"from\": 5869, \"to\": 5880}, {\"ngram\": \"water and sewer upgrades\", \"from\": 5894, \"to\": 5918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wunderley and Charleston Waterkeeper, represented by the Southern Environmental Law Center, earlier this yearthreatened to sueCharleston Water System, 